description.narrative: UNICEF continued to position itself as one of the lead communication and advocacy agencies in Jordan in driving positive change for children, and in delivering on UNICEF’s programmatic priorities.;The COVID-19 pandemic was an opportunity for UNICEF (using web, media and social media) to assert itself as a credible, evidence-based source of information for children and parents around COVID-19.
